divs: Sighting DetailsAll 4 witnesses, were sent to variouse government facilities. She and her two daughters were returned like they were made retarded from "medication" or something. I was sent to U of Iowa and forced into a government program something like, Artichoke! We watched this LARGE object somewhat diamond shaped, come from the East of us and moved West. It appeared to be very slow! The mother of the two girls called the police aboute it. It was out of sight when Officer Barclay arrived. Both side of my grandparants have sighted things in the past. Grandma Pearl, "had close encounters & communications"! She said they promised to take her when she died. The day of her funeral, multiple reports of sightings happened in , Muscatine.
